55
00:03:41,032 --> 00:03:42,902
<font color="yellow">Apa kau masih belum sadar...</font>

56
00:03:45,462 --> 00:03:46,632
<font color="yellow">Apa kau sudah selesai?</font>

57
00:03:48,032 --> 00:03:50,162
<font color="yellow">Kau tidak hanya merusak hidupnya,</font>

