61
00:04:03,962 --> 00:04:05,532
<font color="yellow">sampai kita mendapatkan hasil tesnya.</font>

62
00:04:07,332 --> 00:04:08,632
<font color="yellow">Diam saja terlebih dahulu.</font>

63
00:04:10,702 --> 00:04:12,162
<font color="yellow">Ini adalah kesempatan terakhir...</font>

64
00:04:14,502 --> 00:04:15,872
<font color="yellow">yang aku berikan kepadamu, Paman Tae Cheol.</font>

65
00:04:40,062 --> 00:04:41,162
<font color="yellow">Shim.</font>

66
00:04:51,872 --> 00:04:54,932
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kau lakukan di lingkunganku?</font>

67
00:04:58,032 --> 00:04:59,872
<font color="yellow">Aku sedang menunggumu, Shim.</font>

68
