157
00:12:04,602 --> 00:12:05,802
<font color="yellow">ke taman hiburan besok.</font>

158
00:12:08,562 --> 00:12:09,562
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

159
00:12:10,402 --> 00:12:11,602
<font color="yellow">Besok?</font>

